@RemoteControlApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5067

### Send notification (JSON)
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/send-notification-json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello",
  "body": "Test from http file",
  "link": "https://example.com",
  "targetVersion": "1.2.3",
  "fileName": "note.txt",
  "fileBase64": "SGVsbG8gd29ybGQ="
}

### Send notification (multipart form-data)
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/send-notification
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Hello from multipart
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Message body
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="targetVersion"

1.2.3
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="note.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< note.txt
--MyBoundary--

### Get notifications
GET {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/get-notifications

### Clear notifications
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/clear-notifications

### Stream notifications (SSE)
GET {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/notifications-stream

### Report device version
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/devices/demo-device/version
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.2.3",
  "cardCode": "CARD001"
}

### Fetch notifications for device
GET {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/devices/demo-device/notifications?includeRead=false

### Mark notification as read
# Replace NOTIFICATION_ID with the value returned by the fetch endpoint
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/devices/demo-device/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID/read

### Get app version info
GET {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/app-version

### Upload new app version
POST {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/app-version/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="version"

1.2.3
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="app.apk"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< app.apk
--MyBoundary--

### Download app version
GET {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/app-version/download

### Check app version metadata
HEAD {{RemoteControlApi_HostAddress}}/api/Control/app-version/download
